sources.description:
Beyond "Psycho" SPASMO! 
While walking along the beach, Christian and his girlfriend discover a mysterious woman washed ashore. The following day, Christian meets the woman again at a yacht party and soon finds himself entangled in a web of lust, intrigue and murder.

Original title: Spasmo (1974)


This film is available with many audio & subtitles options.  Go to settings ⚙️ to select your language options.

Director: Umberto Lenzi
Writers: Pino Boller, Massimo Franciosa, Luisa Montagnana
Main Cast: Robert Hoffmann, Suzy Kendall, Ivan Rassimov, Adolfo Lastretti
Genres: Italian cinema, Giallo, Horror, Mystery, Thriller
